{
  "texts": [
    "It can be improved by applying suitable feature selection strategies to perform prediction with the most informative features.",
    "As machine learning algorithms predict the output by learning the relationship between input features and class labels based on classical theories of probability and logic, the accuracy rate is still on the lower side 33, 34.",
    "So, it requires a lot of improvements to have general acceptability for disease prediction.",
    "Another major issue in traditional machine learning algorithms is computation time.",
    "Since the computation time is increased with an increase in the size of the feature set."
  ]
}